WEBVTT

00:04:27.598 --> 00:04:34.295
and in that road were more than 12,000 red chairs,

00:04:34.295 --> 00:04:35.921
empty,

00:04:35.921 --> 00:04:38.190
and every single one of them symbolized

00:04:38.190 --> 00:04:41.907
a person who had died during the siege,

00:04:41.907 --> 00:04:46.194
just in Sarajevo, not in all of Bosnia,

00:04:46.194 --> 00:04:48.781
and it stretched from one end of the city

00:04:48.781 --> 00:04:51.055
to a large part of it,

00:04:51.055 --> 00:04:54.558
and the saddest for me were the tiny little chairs

00:04:54.558 --> 00:04:57.414
for the children.

00:04:57.414 --> 00:05:00.541
I now cover Syria,